Connectivity
============

There are many connectivity options available on the |product| industrial PC. It has 4 x USB3.0 Type A connectors configured as HOSTS, 1 x HDMI port, 1 x DP, 2 x RJ45 connectors supporting Gigabit Ethernet (GbE), and 6 x UART connectors that can be configured in RS485 mode (4 x RS232 + 2 x RS485) as per request.

RS232/485 Connectors
-------------------------

Product has 6 x 9-pin D-Sub connectors. The 2 ports: COM1~COM2, can be configured as either RS232, RS485 or RS422 communication interfaces through BIOS. The 4 ports: COM3/4/5/6 are RS232. If different configuration is required, please get in touch with Chipsee technical support at |email|_

+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| .. centered:: Pin Definition (COM1 COM2 support RS232/485/422)                                                            |
+========================+==================================================================================================+
| **Pin 1**              | DCD/RS485-B/RS422_TX-                                                                            |
+------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| **Pin 2**              | RXD/RS485-A/RS422_TX+                                                                            |
+------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| **Pin 3**              | TXD/RS422_RX+                                                                                    |
+------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| **Pin 4**              | DTR#/RS422_RX-                                                                                   |
+------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+

+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| .. centered:: Pin Definition (COM3/4/5/6 support RS232)                                                                    |
+========================+===================================================================================================+
| **Pin 2**              | RXD                                                                                               |
+------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| **Pin 3**              | TXD                                                                                               |
+------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| **Pin 5**              | GND                                                                                               |
+------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+

